<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt-5">
            <h3>Package Deals!</h3>
            <p>Picking a tour with your room can give you a discount depending on what room type you select..</p>
            Single + Tour = 10% Off <br />
            Double + Tour = 20% Off<br />
            Family Suite + Tour = 40% Off <br /></p>
            <small>Packages will be automatically applied upon successfull booking..</small>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>